  "keyFeatures": [
    "STM32H7 HAL and LL peripheral drivers for all major peripherals (GPIO, UART, SPI, I2C, ADC, DAC, TIM, DMA, etc.)",
    "CMSIS Core and Device support for Arm Cortex-M7 and dual-core Cortex-M7/M4 variants",
    "Board Support Package (BSP) for all official ST Nucleo, Evaluation, and Discovery kits",
    "Integrated middleware: FreeRTOS, LwIP TCP/IP stack, FatFs file system, USB Host/Device, mbedTLS, OpenAMP",
    "Ready-to-build example projects, application templates, and demonstration firmware for each supported board",
    "Dual-core (Cortex-M7 + Cortex-M4) project support with inter-processor communication via OpenAMP and HSEM",
    "Extended memory execution support (ExtMem_CodeExecution) for external Flash/RAM"
  ],
  "publicApiSurface": [
